query:
SELECT
            DATE_TRUNC('hour', updated_at) AS updated_at,
            location.name as location,
            COUNT(*) as count
        FROM
            market_order,   
            location
        WHERE
            location_id = location.id
            AND expires_at > NOW()
        GROUP BY
            DATE_TRUNC('hour', updated_at),
            location
        ORDER BY
            updated_at DESC
